          <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Our courses in Conflict Management, Lone Worker Safety, and Safeguarding are designed to give your staff practical tools while ensuring your organisation meets its statutory obligations.</p>
          <a href="/about/" class="btn btn-secondary">About Our Approach</a>
        </div>
        <div class="info-image">
